◇ Padma Bhasha Standard Token Contract
◇ Secondary Bridged Asset: PYAR 

सूत्र मुख्य {
    √सृज्+ति·नाम ← "KasturiChain Pyar"
    √सृज्+ति·naman ← "PYAR"
    √सृज्+ति·sankhya ← 0  ◇ Starts at 0, only minted via the Bridge
    
    ◇ Initialize balances map
    √सृज्+ति·kosha ← {}
}

◇ Only the Bridge  can mint new secondary PYAR
सूत्र mint {
    √लभ्+ति·preshakah ← ◈
    
    ◇ Access Control: Only the registered Bridge address can call mint
    यदि  {
        प्रतिदा "दोष: Only Setu Bridge can mint"
    }

    ◇ Increase total supply
    √सृज्+ति·sankhya ← sankhya + matra
    
    ◇ Add to receiver's balance
    यदि  {
        √सृज्+ति·kosha[grahakah] ← matra
    } अन्यथा {
        √सृज्+ति·kosha[grahakah] ← kosha[grahakah] + matra
    }
    
    √वच्+ति·सन्देश ← "Minted PYAR via Bridge"
    प्रतिदा 108
}

◇ Standard transfer function for secondary PYAR
सूत्र transfer {
    √लभ्+ति·preshakah ← ◈
    
    यदि  {
        प्रतिदा "दोष: Insufficient secondary PYAR balance"
    }
    
    √सृज्+ति·kosha[preshakah] ← kosha[preshakah] - matra
    
    यदि  {
        √सृज्+ति·kosha[grahakah] ← matra
    } अन्यथा {
        √सृज्+ति·kosha[grahakah] ← kosha[grahakah] + matra
    }
    
    प्रतिदा 108
}

